'''Avatar Museum''' is a long-running virtual exhibition primarily for [[avatars]], providing a platform for showcasing avatars and other [[VRChat]] content in a simple environment made by おおかみちゃん. Across all the iterations, the museum always looks similar. The content is from thousands of creators, and the avatars are primarily aimed at PC users. Some worlds are dedicated to Quest Avatars or assets for avatars like clothes and items.

