==Submissions==
Links to technical limitations can be found on the Homepage. Submissions need to contain a <code>unitypackage</code> which gets generated with an extra tool in Unity that needs to be [https://w01fa.booth.pm/items/2622659 downloaded].

The deadline is about 1 month before the world goes public.

